creator: Grata Pro
descriptionHtml: Grata is the only recognition platform designed to connect the community of customers and the terrific employees who serve them. Our Uber exit-like experience is a frictionless way for the hard work and efforts of 80M+ hourly employees to get the recognition and money they deserve. As customers, we get our favorite go-to list of the employees who treat us well so we can always get the service we deserve (not to mention, all the free stuff!). As employers, we finally have qualitative data on our frontline staff to ensure we are developing, rewarding, and serving our customers better.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: 80 million service-sector employees in the U.S. alone have no permanent record of their hard work or accomplishments. There is not a LinkedIn for those of us who serve food, repair cars, babysit or work in retail. Well, that is, until now. Grata is a Yelp-like rating system designed to a knowledge the efforts of the largest working class in America. As a waiter, you can now get your great work documented. As a patron, you can build your list of people who treat you best.

We’ve made a bunch of changes to make getting and receiving Gratas easier for you and your whole team!

Changes include:
⁃ Your unique QR code now pops up automatically, making it easier to share your code to get recognition and praise
⁃ A new Peers Page where you can easily see your whole organization and find co-workers to give a peer Grata to
⁃ A brand new Feed Page where you can see all the Gratas you and your peers are giving and receiving all in one place
